Name: 10mg: HANDMADEDEATHLABYRINTH issue 0
About the game: 10mg is a collection of 10 minute long games. HANDMADEDEATHLABYRINTH issue 0 is one of them: an unforgiving little adventure full of monsters that should take about 10 minutes to finish. From start to end, you'll get a specific, singular expression of the dungeon crawl experience; the hero's journey is to descend into the depths, ignoring their fears, and return a different person. What will you find down there? What you'll find in the labyrinth One sword. One dungeon to crawl that stays the same every time you die. Anything else you find down there, you keep.
